{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EF1BG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EF1BG_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
State nonprofit corporation statutes typically permit amendments to corporate charters, including purposes clauses, as long as the entity follows the proper internal procedures.
}
