{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 In other words, the typical nonprofit corporation statute does not forbid members or directors from changing the historic charter purposes of an incorporated charity.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
