96
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Thus, state nonprofit corporation statutes commonly appear to embrace the dynamic charter fidelity norm as applied to the formal requirements for amending a corporate charter.
}
