{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 applied the dynamic charter fidelity norm in one context and the static charter fidelity norm in another. First, the court held that the corporate charity\rquote s board did not violate any fiduciary duty 
