{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Because donors were on notice under the corporation\rquote s bylaws that its purposes could be expanded to include additional purposes for which the affiliated trust was organized, and further because two amendments to the charter conformed to trust purposes, the court found that these amendments were consistent with the terms of trust,
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F131398601898_ID0EPKAI_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F131398601898_ID0EPKAI_1}
