*939
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb400 
 and responsibility to \u8220\'3fenforce the due application of [charitable] funds ... and prevent breaches of trust in the administration thereof.\u8221\'3f
}
