{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 In 1971, Queen\rquote s board of directors approved a lease of the hospital facilities (except for the outpatient clinic and a convent house) to a for-profit company.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F137398601898_ID0EVOAI_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F137398601898_ID0EVOAI_1}
