{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Opposing the deal, California\rquote s Attorney General argued \u8220\'3fthat under its articles of incorporation, Queen held its assets in trust primarily for the purpose of operating a hospital, and the use of those assets exclusively for outpatient clinics would constitute an abandonment of Queen\rquote s primary charitable purpose and a diversion of charitable trust assets.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
