}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 In 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Blocker
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
, the court held that the directors of a charitable corporation breached their fiduciary duties by attempting to distribute corporate assets in dissolution to a private estate in which several directors had a personal interest.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
