{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Although the holding itself is unremarkable, its rationale is potentially far-reaching. The court accepted the state\rquote s argument that the charter of a charitable corporation constitutes a declaration of charitable trust.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
