{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The court held that property transferred to a charitable corporation is \u8220\'3fsubject to implicit charitable or educational limitations 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
defined by the donee\rquote s organizational purpose
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 and within the meaning of the statute, where no express limitation to the contrary is stated in the transfer.\u8221\'3f
