{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 According to the court, property that could be traced to such assets was likewise held by the charity \u8220\'3fsubject to the limitations imposed on 
}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_1530_946_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_1530_946_1}
