*946
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 the corporation by the terms of its own articles of incorporation.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F196398601898_ID0EVGBI_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F196398601898_ID0EVGBI_1}
