197
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The provision generally required a dissolving nonprofit corporation to transfer such assets upon dissolution to organizations engaged in activities substantially similar to those in which the dissolving entity had engaged.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
